            <div class="row">
                <div class="col text-break">
                            <h2>Role description</h2>
                            <p class="text-break white-space-pre-line">At RCL FOODS we grow what matters Our Talent Team is looking for someone who is brilliant at the basics to fill the role of Distribution Controller with great attention to detail skills to join our Baking Operating Unit . The role will report to the Distribution Manager and will be based in Rustenburg. The primary function and responsibility of a Site Controller is to ensure that all Drivers and Van assistants report to duty on time and that trucks are dispatched on time and in full. Vehicles returning from trade are debriefed correctly and efficiently in line with company procedures. That all stock receiving/returned in saleable condition is checked, documented, and isolated into the relevant cage and is marked labelled correctly to ensure it is returned to the correct truck. Stock to be written off/disposed is then checked and documented before being removed. To manage the fleet operations team in order to ensure high performance and innovative thinking through the implementation of all people processes in line with agreed KPI’s and budgets To support the Sales Rep in providing adequate route optimisation and rationalisation solutions. To ensure our customer needs are met within a viable business framework. To provide a link between despatch and drivers for a seamless transition of products. To provide key trade intel and address regular customer service requirements.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
